{"tid":793371,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"同條女搞野遇到呢個問題","createTime":"2018-08-25T11:10:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-27T10:44:15.000Z","uid":151836,"like":39,"dislike":415,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"009034288cfb5c6e67e0ddeb0398268cc8f3a9fb","tid":793371,"uid":151836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T11:10:23.000Z","msg":"早排同女朋友搞野個陣時興起想奶閪<br />\n<br />\n點知一隊個頭埋去就聞到陣鹹魚味 <br />\n<br />\n陣味就好似一條醃左10年嘅鹹魚再醃多10年 <br />\n<br />\n之後我頂硬上奶咗一野 已經縮返個頭走<br />\n<br />\n點知條仆街仲要問做咩啊bb  <br />\n<br />\n聽到呢句真係火到黎 我即刻開佢波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>好撚臭</strong></span><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>好撚臭</strong></span><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>真係好撚臭啊 仆街</strong></span><br />\n咁我當然無講出口<br />\n咪話 無野 食到毛 哈哈<br />\n<br />\n佢竟然仲叫我 咁繼續啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我咪話唔啦下次先 好攰<br />\n<br />\n結果佢反問我 你而家係咪嫌棄我啊？<br />\n<br />\n屌 條仆街都講到咁 我唯有認命委屈下<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後想問下巴打 邊到有好撚柒臭嘅鹹魚可以買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64eb4a99d2346931603edb29c46480cb1fcd3a52","tid":793371,"uid":152147,"like":314,"dislike":0,"score":314,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T11:11:45.000Z","msg":"冇是咁的 0分重作"},{"pid":"332d0a3675cab902858de79d9888cbcf92a2a156","tid":793371,"uid":50744,"like":168,"dislike":2,"score":166,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T11:12:53.000Z","msg":"2/10<br />\n抄多過作"},{"pid":"53b52f96eab02d9c60a89637f2a7f9cdf80fa7ef","tid":793371,"uid":151836,"like":0,"dislike":35,"score":-35,"quote":{"pid":"332d0a3675cab902858de79d9888cbcf92a2a156","tid":793371,"uid":50744,"like":168,"dislike":2,"score":166,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T11:12:53.000Z","msg":"2/10<br />\n抄多過作"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T11:13:58.000Z","msg":"真人真事"},{"pid":"967a372b07e40234820b0adc63c78d9bb8a2c98b","tid":793371,"uid":15